reviewText: The story is dumb & childish. It also slow the plot down. The jokes are lame & cheesy. The villans are obvious & phoned a mile away. I will give the wrestlers credit for calling the cops when the time was right. Hulk Hogan getting mad in this episode reminds me how Hulk got mad in Mr. Nanny expect in this show it's more funny then scary. I give the "rent me" 3 out of 10.
